{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Publish all OBR forecasts immediately once received by the Government",
        "additional_details": "We believe the first responsibility of government in a democratic society is to protect and safeguard the lives of its citizens. Some current government actions in isolation do help in this regard but the totality of announcements in the mini-budget are already causing immoral hardship and insecurity for many. For this reason we believe it is important to publish OBR forecasts immediately. ",
        "background": "We ask that all future OBR forecasts be made publicly available on the same day as the Government is in receipt of them.",
